snippet.title: The Dark Phantom Trailer
snippet.description:
A fast-paced third person shooter narrating a neo-noir story enhanced by a dark and comic style art set in a criminal infested city.
The Darkphantom is a 3D third person shooter powered by UDK technology with emphasis on covering and dynamic gun fights. The player will play in the role of The Dark Phantom, angel of night and voice of justice, a man robbed of his past, seeking light in the darkness. 
Follow us on facebook: https://www.facebook.com/dawnofdarknessGame
